s/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-say-pro-netanyahu-channel-told-them-coalition-trumps-deal/00000191-bd90-dffe-abf9-bdff65c90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列处于战争状态，第 334 天：大约 70 枚火箭从黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</link><description>政府消息人士告诉《国土报》，内塔尼亚胡几周前决定不达成释放人质协议，并以费城走廊为借口破坏谈判。据《华尔街日报》报道，预计将提交更详细的人质/停火协议草案 ■ 这是战争开始 334 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 17:00:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-334-some-70-rockets-fired-at-north-israel-from-lebanon/00000191-bdf0-dc3b-a7df-fff0b3620001</guid></item><item><title>为什么哈马斯试图隐瞒被以色列杀害的武装分子人数</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</link><description>所有加沙人都知道不要发布被杀的哈马斯战士的信息，任何违反这一规则的人都有可能给该组织以及以色列带来麻烦</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:57:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-hamas-tries-to-hide-the-number-of-its-members-killed/00000191-bd7b-d13c-a39b-bfff809b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列教育部禁止学校举办以色列-巴勒斯坦遇难者家庭论坛</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-bans-schools-from-hosting-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum/00000191-bd5b-d227-aff3-bfdbb1fe0000</link><description>以色列教育部无视耶路撒冷地方法院的命令，冻结了一个“对话遭遇”计划，该计划由一个将失去亲人的巴勒斯坦和以色列家庭聚集在一起的组织运营。</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 16:22:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/education-ministry-bans-schools-from-hosting-israeli-palestinian-bereaved-families-forum/00000191-bd5b-d227-aff3-bfdbb1fe0000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔交通事故调查员出席部长聚会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/investigator-of-ben-gvirs-traffic-accident-attended-ministers-party/00000191-bd07-dc3b-a7df-ff57acfd0000</link><description>负责该部门的警官预计将就这起事故起诉本-格维尔的司机 ■ 警方表示，他只在现场出现了几分钟，且原因无关</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:48:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/investigator-of-ben-gvirs-traffic-accident-attended-ministers-party/00000191-bd07-dc3b-a7df-ff57acfd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方关闭特拉维夫抗议空域以“监控空中交通”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-to-close-airspace-over-tel-aviv-protest-to-monitor-air-traffic/00000191-bd15-d13c-a39b-bf9db7d70000</link><description>来自“示范无人机巡逻队”的无人机传单在过去两年里一直在从上方记录演示，他们声称这是一个旨在让他们更难操作的步骤</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:12:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-to-close-airspace-over-tel-aviv-protest-to-monitor-air-traffic/00000191-bd15-d13c-a39b-bf9db7d70000</guid></item><item><title>愤怒的以色列人正在抗议以拯救人质。他们能改变内塔尼亚胡的想法吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/furious-israelis-are-protesting-to-save-the-hostages-can-they-change-netanyahus-mind/00000191-bc49-d9c6-a997-be6996320000</link><description>自周日以来，以色列人为人质发起了大规模的公民动员：数十万人走上街头，举行总罢工。尽管哈马斯杀害了更多人质，但示威者并不能迫使内塔尼亚胡政府放弃对一项挽救生命的协议的抵制</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 14:07:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/furious-israelis-are-protesting-to-save-the-hostages-can-they-change-netanyahus-mind/00000191-bc49-d9c6-a997-be6996320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长突然腾出时间制定国家预算</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-suddenly-finds-time-for-the-state-budget/00000191-bd19-de3d-abb7-ff7bdc6c0000</link><description>在一再拖延之后，斯莫特里奇决定是时候公布 2025 年的支出计划了。他是终于清醒过来了，还是陷入了恐慌？</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 13:18:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israels-finance-minister-suddenly-finds-time-for-the-state-budget/00000191-bd19-de3d-abb7-ff7bdc6c0000</guid></item><item><title>我父亲是加沙的人质。我必须恳求内塔尼亚胡拯救他吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-do-i-have-to-beg-netanyahu-to-save-him/00000191-bcec-db99-a1d1-bdfe774c0000</link><description>早在十月份，我们就非常确信我们的政府会尽一切努力拯救人质，首先是从最脆弱的人开始，比如你，爸爸。我听到你告诉我：“救救孩子们吧，我已经过上了充实的生活。”但内塔尼亚胡政府并没有拯救孩子们，也没有拯救你这个84岁的老人</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:47:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-father-is-a-hostage-in-gaza-do-i-have-to-beg-netanyahu-to-save-him/00000191-bcec-db99-a1d1-bdfe774c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军告诉家长，黎巴嫩边境 75% 的以色列军队观察员已从前线撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</link><description>以色列国防军观察员的父母向以色列高等法院请愿，回应驻黎巴嫩边境观察员的投诉，称他们的基地在真主党袭击中避难所不足，并且担心类似于哈马斯 10 月 7 日对纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所实施的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</guid></item><item><title>“他脱掉裤子并说‘过来看看’”：希伯伦的巴勒斯坦妇女报告遭到以色列士兵的骚扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/female-palestinian-hebron-residents-claim-harassment-by-israeli-soldiers/00000191-bc9e-d9c6-a997-bebe2ae40000</link><description>一名来自约旦河西岸城市希伯伦的妇女最近报告称遭到一名以色列士兵的骚扰。其他女性表示这不是一起孤立事件，并讲述了辱骂和未经授权搜查手机的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/female-palestinian-hebron-residents-claim-harassment-by-israeli-soldiers/00000191-bc9e-d9c6-a997-bebe2ae40000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报托马斯·弗里德曼表示，内塔尼亚胡升级加沙战争以帮助特朗普赢得选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/netanyahu-escalating-gaza-war-to-help-trump-win-elections-nyts-thomas-friedman-says/00000191-bc6b-dd1b-a7db-bfffdf070000</link><description>《纽约时报》专栏作家托马斯·弗里德曼认为，内塔尼亚胡在加沙协议谈判期间做出的决定是为了在即将到来的选举中强化特朗普，他认为特朗普将在政治上帮助他</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/netanyahu-escalating-gaza-war-to-help-trump-win-elections-nyts-thomas-friedman-says/00000191-bc6b-dd1b-a7db-bfffdf070000</guid></item><item><title>联盟消息来源：内塔尼亚胡几周前决定反对人质交易，并发现费城是一个有效的旋转</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/coalition-source-netanyahu-decided-against-hostage-deal-weeks-ago-philadelphi-is-a-spin/00000191-bc3a-dc3b-a7df-ff7a0ab60000</link><description>就像一个真正的独裁者一样，总理正在拿人质的生命开玩笑。部长和议员们仍然袖手旁观，不采取任何行动来拯救人质，其中一些人发表了强烈声明支持达成协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/coalition-source-netanyahu-decided-against-hostage-deal-weeks-ago-philadelphi-is-a-spin/00000191-bc3a-dc3b-a7df-ff7a0ab60000</guid></item><item><title>在共和党与犹太人的会议上，共和党将支持内塔尼亚胡对哈马斯和拜登的“全面胜利”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-republican-jewish-confab-gop-set-to-back-netanyahus-total-victory-over-hamas-and-biden/00000191-b8ca-de3d-abb7-feeb37410000</link><description>发言人名单包括埃莉斯·斯特凡尼克（Elise Stefanik）、大卫·弗里德曼（David Friedman）和米里亚姆·阿德尔森（Miriam Adelson），在拉斯维加斯举行的共和党犹太联盟年度聚会上，共和党人可能会支持以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的加沙政策，同时指责拜登造成人质死亡</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-republican-jewish-confab-gop-set-to-back-netanyahus-total-victory-over-hamas-and-biden/00000191-b8ca-de3d-abb7-feeb37410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方过去两天拒绝释放50多名被拘留的抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-refuse-to-release-over-50-detained-protesters-over-past-two-days/00000191-bbdd-d13c-a39b-bfdd5d3a0000</link><description>在几乎所有案件中，法院都拒绝了警方延长抗议者拘留期限的请求。在某些案件中，法官批评警方没有提供针对被捕者的证据，或者提供的证据特别少</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-refuse-to-release-over-50-detained-protesters-over-past-two-days/00000191-bbdd-d13c-a39b-bfdd5d3a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国仍在谈论人质交易，但私下对内塔尼亚胡感到绝望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-still-talking-about-a-hostage-deal-but-israeli-intransigence-increases-frustration/00000191-ba19-d13c-a39b-be9d9db20000</link><description>华盛顿官员承认，政府为维持停火谈判所做的努力“与现实没有真正的联系”</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 03:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/u-s-still-talking-about-a-hostage-deal-but-israeli-intransigence-increases-frustration/00000191-ba19-d13c-a39b-be9d9db20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡：“如果你想释放人质，你就必须控制费城”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-live/u-s-unseals-charges-against-6-hamas-leaders-for-oct-7-attack-vows-more-measures-to-come/00000191-bac4-dc3b-a7df-fbd4abb60000</link><description>美国新提案确定以色列可以在费城路线停留多久 ■ 人质家属在特拉维夫利库德集团总部前抗议 ■ 甘茨称费城走廊对以色列不构成生存威胁 ■ 拉皮德称结束战争符合以色列的利益，但政府更喜欢战争 ■ 黎巴嫩火箭弹袭击后，以色列北部爆发火灾</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 02:13:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-live/u-s-unseals-charge